data.description: This 4-bed, 2-bath Craftsman-style home offers 1175 sqft of modern living. The open living area features a spacious gathering room, an airy kitchen with a counter-height island and walk-in pantry, and a sunny dining cafe. The owner's suite includes a luxurious bath with dual vanities, a garden tub, tiled shower, and a walk-in wardrobe with ample storage. Additional highlights include a drop-zone, dedicated laundry room, and a front porch with a covered lanai. Secondary bedrooms share a convenient hall bath and linen closet, making this home perfect for comfortable, stylish living.
